{"id":1134,"date":"2022-02-11T17:14:00","date_gmt":"2022-02-11T17:14:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1134"},"modified":"2022-02-11T12:26:20","modified_gmt":"2022-02-11T12:26:20","slug":"manage-layered-storage","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1134","title":{"rendered":"Manage layered storage"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 id=\"understand-the-advanced-storage\">Understand the advanced storage<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"475\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?resize=640%2C475&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1143\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?w=670&amp;ssl=1 670w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?resize=300%2C223&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?resize=24%2C18&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?resize=36%2C27&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-94.png?resize=48%2C36&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>LVM and STRATIS are very similar, but STRATIS is newer and more advanced. All of them have their own use cases, and you could google them out, but for now let&#8217;s just focus on STRATIS. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"managing-layered-local-storage-with-stratis\">MANAGING LAYERED LOCAL STORAGE WITH STRATIS<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"what-is-stratis\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tecmint.com\/install-stratis-to-manage-layered-local-storage-on-rhel\/\">What is Stratis<\/a><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Stratis<\/strong>&nbsp;is one of the new features that ships with&nbsp;<strong>RHEL 8<\/strong>&nbsp;distribution.&nbsp;<strong>Stratis<\/strong>&nbsp;is a local storage management solution that focuses on simplicity and improved usability while at the same time providing access to advanced storage features. It uses the XFS file system and grants you access to advanced storage capabilities such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Thin provisioning<\/li><li>File system snapshots<\/li><li>Tiering<\/li><li>Pool-based management<\/li><li>Monitoring<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Basically,&nbsp;<strong>Stratis<\/strong>&nbsp;is a storage pool that is created from one or more local disks or disk partitions. Stratis helps a System administrator set up and manage complex storage configurations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we proceed further, let us have a look at some of the technical terms you are bound to bump into as we go along:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>pool<\/strong>: A pool is made up of one or more block devices. The total size of the pool is equal to the sum total of the block devices.<\/li><li><strong>blockdev<\/strong>: As you might have guessed it this refers to block devices such as disk partitions.<\/li><li><strong>Filesystem<\/strong>: A filesystem is a thinly provisioned layer which does not come as a total fixed size. The filesystem\u2019s actual size grows as data is added. Stratis automatically grows the size of the filesystem as data size nears the virtual size of the file system.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Block devices that you can use with Stratis include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>LVM Logical Volumes<\/li><li>LUKS<\/li><li>SSDs (Solid State Drives)<\/li><li>Device Mapper Multipath<\/li><li>iSCSI<\/li><li>HDDs (Hard Disk Drives)<\/li><li>mdraid<\/li><li>NVMe storage devices<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"installation-of-stratis\">Installation of STRATIS<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Update the OS first<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">yum update &amp;&amp; yum upgrade -y<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>After that install stratis and all the necessary packages <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">yum install stratisd stratis-cli<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And start the service<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"272\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?resize=640%2C272&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1135\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?w=740&amp;ssl=1 740w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?resize=300%2C128&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?resize=24%2C10&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?resize=36%2C15&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-86.png?resize=48%2C20&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"configuration-of-stratis\">Configuration of STRATIS<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>List out available space with lsblk<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"627\" height=\"292\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?resize=627%2C292&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1136\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?w=627&amp;ssl=1 627w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?resize=300%2C140&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?resize=24%2C11&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?resize=36%2C17&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-87.png?resize=48%2C22&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Look&#8217;s like disk \/dev\/sdc is free so let&#8217;s use that one. First we need to create a pool for STRATIS, to do that type<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis pool create PoolTest \/dev\/sdc<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And list this new pool with <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis pool list<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"108\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?resize=640%2C108&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?w=730&amp;ssl=1 730w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?resize=300%2C51&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?resize=36%2C6&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-88.png?resize=48%2C8&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next step is creating a filesystem on top of the STRATIS. STRATIS explicitly use XFS only<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis filesystem create PoolTest FileSystemTest<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And list it out with <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis filesystem list<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"108\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?resize=640%2C108&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1138\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?w=729&amp;ssl=1 729w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?resize=300%2C51&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?resize=36%2C6&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-89.png?resize=48%2C8&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"mounting-a-filesystem\">Mounting a filesystem<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Create some folder to mount the filesystem to and mount it with mount command<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">mkdir \/mnt\/sratis_test<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">mount \/dev\/stratis\/PoolTest\/FileSystemTest \/mnt\/stratis_test<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"permanently-mounting-the-stratis-filesystem\">Permanently mounting the STRATIS filesystem<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">vi \/etc\/fstab<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"151\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=640%2C151&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1139\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=1024%2C242&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=300%2C71&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=768%2C181&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=24%2C6&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=36%2C9&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?resize=48%2C11&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-90.png?w=1029&amp;ssl=1 1029w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"working-with-stratis\">Working with STRATIS<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If we typed df -h, we would see our STRATIS filesystem, but it would display some not accurate number of disk space. This is because tools like VDO or STRATIS don&#8217;t play well with df command, and we need to use their own tool commands<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"104\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=640%2C104&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1141\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=1024%2C167&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=768%2C126&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=36%2C6&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?resize=48%2C8&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-92.png?w=1297&amp;ssl=1 1297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The command use for STRATIS listing is<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis blockdev<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"445\" height=\"75\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?resize=445%2C75&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1142\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?w=445&amp;ssl=1 445w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?resize=300%2C51&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?resize=36%2C6&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-93.png?resize=48%2C8&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 445px) 100vw, 445px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"creating-snapshots-with-stratis\">Creating snapshots with STRATIS<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the many advantages STRATIS has, it&#8217;s creating snapshot as a backup for the system. Let&#8217;s try out and create a text file which we will SNAPSHOT and try to recover.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">echo \"HEUREKAAA, this is working\" > \/mnt\/stratis_test\/test_file.txt<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use stratis fs to list out all of our STRATIS filesystems<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis fs<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"42\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=640%2C42&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1145\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=1024%2C67&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=300%2C20&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=768%2C50&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=24%2C2&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=36%2C2&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?resize=48%2C3&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-95.png?w=1259&amp;ssl=1 1259w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To create a snapshot type<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis filesystem snapshot <em>my-pool<\/em> <em>my-fs<\/em> <em>my-fs-backup<\/em><\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"78\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=640%2C78&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1146\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=1024%2C125&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=300%2C37&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=768%2C94&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=36%2C4&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?w=1347&amp;ssl=1 1347w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-96.png?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s umount oldfile system and mount a new one<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"81\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=640%2C81&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1147\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?w=837&amp;ssl=1 837w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=300%2C38&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=768%2C97&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=36%2C5&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-97.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Heyy it&#8217;s working!!!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"remove-old-filesystem\">Remove old filesystem<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">stratis filesystem destroy pool_name Filesytem_name<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"73\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-98.png?resize=640%2C73&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1148\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-98.png?resize=1024%2C117&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-98.png?resize=300%2C34&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/up